### February 2025 Summary for scaffold-eth/create-eth-extensions

- **New Features and Improvements:**
  - Added new templates to enhance functionality (#54).
  - Implemented verification for OP Retro Funding round 7 (#53).
  - Updated `subgraph` extension modules, including upgrades to `graph-cli` and `graph-node` (#51).

- **Closed Pull Requests:**
  - One pull request was closed without merging, focusing on updating example configurations (#52).

- **Overall Themes:**
  - The month saw a focus on enhancing templates and module updates, indicating ongoing development and maintenance of the repository. No issues were reported or created during this period.

topPRs.title: Add OP Retro Funding round 7 verification
